text: Yilian Olivera Yut (born 27 July 1983) is a Cuban female volleyball player. She played for the Cuba women's national volleyball team. She participated at the 2002 Pan American Cup and 2002 FIVB World Grand Prix. == References == == Other websites == * yilian-olivera-yut , worldofvolley.com Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban volleyball players
